(31, 28, 'add_description', 'Guided Reading\r\nJust add leveled books and this resource contains everything you need to conduct successful, engaging Guided Reading group lessons. This best selling resource includes:\r\n* Reading Strategy Posters for Guided Reading lessons\r\n* Trading Cards to reinforce the learning at home\r\n*Word Work activities and printables to reinforce the strategies. These can be used during Guided Reading lessons and during independent work time. \r\n*Comprehension activities and printables that can be used during Guided Reading lessons or independent time.\r\n*Guided Reading Lesson Plan forms and graphic organizers\r\nRunning Record Forms\r\nand Much More!\r\nNOTE: This unit was revised and added to on 8/21/2014\r\nThanks a bunch, Deanna Jump\r\n\r\nGuided Reading, Word Work, Comprehension, Reading Strategies'),
